    "subject": "Weapon animation issues when entering tank or using MG",
    "description": "There are several issues with this one. The demo shows most of the cases but the one it didn't capture was with Mortar.\r\nHow to reproduce some of these bugs:\r\n- Riflegrenade:\r\n1. Put riflegrenade on\r\n2. Mean the animation is going enter the tank or use MG\r\n3. Leave the tank or MG\r\nor\r\n1. Take the riflegrenade off\r\n2. Mean the animation is going enter the tank or use MG\r\n3. Leave the tank or MG\r\n\r\n- Bazooka/Panzerfaust:\r\n1. Shoot with Panzer\r\n2. Enter tank or MG before you have shot\r\n3. Leave the tank or MG\r\n\r\n- Mortar:\r\n1. Mount Mortar\r\n2. Unmount Mortar\r\n3. During the unmount animation enter the tank\r\n4. Leave the tank\r\n\r\nSee the attached demo for the results. Also there could be other weapons too but I didn't find more for now.\r\n\r\n-*S",
